{"tid":1686310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由一件事已經可以證明香港人根本未準備好全民勇武","createTime":"2019-11-01T04:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T06:00:14.000Z","uid":123720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df88d22ac5f4fa30772d73940c7dfe0c9587dd1a","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"個件事就係屯門兆軒苑<br />\n成班香港人被羞辱 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">跪地式搜身</span></span> 居然毫無反抗<br />\n連咁都唔反抗 證明香港人反抗暫時只係一個口號<br />\n所以最近吹風叫勇武出嚟終極一戰嘅Post好大程度都係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗</span></span>出<br />\n雖然真正勇武都好聰明唔會中伏 但我都係想多口提一句 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家勿中伏呀</span></span><br />\nPs 香港人幾時先反抗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重要幾大嘅核彈先反抗呀"},{"pid":"505f0fdce80c6b5918a2835821f1c77b68a1491c","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:53:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d2c6ac6a633df1f0c753a82e6b71d17c2a76fee","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9b39beb823bb124eb8bb964eedf1a3a86cead0a","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"897883fcc3e6926eeec133af9341d1833d7fbc7c","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88fdd17a40e623780ec885a7727c4cd68028466e","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:30:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6877bbaddf18e9632bd15bcd6c1b85fbd5243e8","tid":1686310,"uid":123720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}